# Change Log
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](http://keepachangelog.com/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).

## [3.1.0]
### Updated
- Removed all debug outputs. Mainly shown in the settings page when WP_DEBUG is enabled. Fixes #4
- Updated all translations functions to use string literals.
- Updates to the admin settings HTML and classes to have a better UI.
- Cleanup settings page titles and descriptions per site.
### Fixes
- When a new site is added, and the network featured image settings haven't been updated, avoid throwing a
fatal error, also fixes #4.
### Added
- Added fallback image for sites on the Network Sites page, which if filterable using
`ms_featured_image_placeholder_image`.

## [3.0.2]
### Updated
-  Missing autoloader for Admin directory

## [3.0.1]
### Added
- Admin notice when no running PHP version >= `7.0.1`.

## [3.0.0]
### Changed
- Updated all files with PSR4 directory structure.
- Cleaned up includes and introduced spl autoload.
- Changed functions to namespace prefix.
### Removed
- Deprecated the 'ignore-blog-id' shortcode attribute in favor of 'ignore-blog-ids'

## [2.1.0] - 2017-04-24
### Changed
- Make sure get all sites only returns public blogs.

## [2.0.0] - 2015-11-19
### Changed
- Complete rewrite.
- Deprecated the four helper functions in favor of better prefixed functions. See
https://frosty.media/?post_type=doc&p=103576 for more info.
- Update TGM Plugin Activation to `v2.5.2`

## [1.0.0] - 2013-11-26
- Initial release.